OL,3,CThe Flying Christine III: Saving lives
OL,4,Con Guernsey's seas for 30 years
OL,6,FThe Channel Islands' only marine
OL,7,Fambulance which has saved more than
OL,8,F1,000 lives is celebrating 30 years of
OL,9,Fservice to Guernsey's seas.
OL,11,FThe Flying Christine III was launched
OL,12,Fin 1994, dedicated to helping those
OL,13,Fwho fall seriously ill at sea.
OL,15,FThe vessel is kitted out with
OL,16,Fstretchers, oxygen and defibrillators
OL,17,Fall onboard to assist patients.
