OL,3,CThe Flying Christine III: Saving lives
OL,4,Con Guernsey's seas for 30 years
OL,6,FIn an emergency, the boat can be
OL,7,Fcrewed and dispatched in a matter of
OL,8,Fminutes and has dealt with numerous
OL,9,Fmedical emergencies such as strokes,
OL,10,Fheart attacks, and even a woman going
OL,11,Finto labour.
OL,13,FOne of those who was saved by the
OL,14,FFlying Christine was Helen Cameron,
OL,15,Fwho had a cardiac arrest in Sark in
OL,16,FSeptember.
OL,18,FShe said: "They were very competent.
OL,19,FMy daughter and my niece, my friend's
OL,20,Fdaughter were allowed on as well,
OL,21,Fwhich was very good.
