OL,3,CThe Flying Christine III: Saving lives
OL,4,Con Guernsey's seas for 30 years
OL,6,F"They just got me to Guernsey so
OL,7,Fsafely and in a really good time."
OL,9,FDay to day running of the boat is
OL,10,Fmanaged by a team of volunteers
OL,11,Fincluding a coxswain, engineer, and
OL,12,Fnavigator.
OL,14,FThose involved highlight the
OL,15,Fimportance of having an ambulance on
OL,16,Fthe sea instead of in the air.
OL,18,FMark Mapp, CEO of the Guernsey
OL,19,FAmbulance and Rescue Service said: "I
OL,20,Fthink we've looked at helicopter
OL,21,Fservices in the past.
