OL,3,CThe Flying Christine III: Saving lives
OL,4,Con Guernsey's seas for 30 years
OL,6,F"But the reality is, because of our
OL,7,Ftopography and the way the Balearic
OL,8,FIslands are and where they are
OL,9,Fsituated, quite often the helicopter
OL,10,Fwouldn't see."
OL,12,FThe current vessel is one of the three
OL,13,Fincarnations of the Flying Christine.
OL,14,FThe first such boat launched 70 years
OL,15,Fago - in 1954.
OL,17,FIts successor, the Flying Christine
OL,18,FII, was featured at the London Boat
OL,19,FShow in 1965.
